As the day winds down, interview sign-up sheets fill with names, and announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair. Alumni volunteers share quick pep talks near the coffee station, and some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. Friends decompress on the quad, comparing which companies responded warmly. Camera crews from the university media team capture interviews during the event, while career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops.

A data science company showcases a live dashboard of fair attendance, while healthcare providers display photos of community outreach efforts. Tech companies feature demo screens for their latest apps, and a robotics startup attracts attention with a small drone flying above its booth. Some students practice their elevator pitches quietly against the wall, and international students queue for advice on visa sponsorship requirements. Representatives from nonprofits emphasize mission-driven career paths. As the day winds down, volunteers stack collapsed booths and gather leftover brochures, while interview sign-up sheets fill.
